documents.technical_details: A set of Bonjour Paris! magnetic figures from Mudpuppy is a package full of portable fun. Dress two figures a la mode and place them in four background scenes, including the Eiffel Tower, Louvre Pyramid, cafe, and street with as patisserie. Illustrated by Bella Pilar. | 1.05 pounds (View shipping rates and policies)
